Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.menus

Interface EditorMenuTraceInfo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditorMenuTraceInfoImpl
    public interface EditorMenuTraceInfo
    The interface representing the editor menu trace info node. While building the transformation or substitute menu the transformation/substitute parts may build the tree of such trace info nodes via TransformationMenuContext.getEditorMenuTrace() or SubstituteMenuContext.getEditorMenuTrace()

    The leaf transformation/substitute items then store the references to the editor menu trace info node so one can trace back the appearance of the item in the menu.

    The node has the references to the parent node, the children nodes and the menu descriptor.

    • Method Detail

      • getMenuDescriptor

        @Nullable
EditorMenuDescriptor getMenuDescriptor()
        The menu descriptor of the editor menu info node. Commonly it is the descriptor provided by the menu part while building the transformation/substitute menu
        Returns:
        the menu descriptor. May be null.

      • getParent

        @Nullable
EditorMenuTraceInfo getParent()
        The parent of the editor menu info node. Commonly it is the info node of the previous transformation/substitute part in the menu building chain. For example if the current node is the node provided by the transformation/substitute part containing in the group part, then the parent node is the node provided by the group part.

        The parent of the root node is null.

        Returns:
        the parent editor menu trace info. May be null.

      • getChildren

        @NotNull
Collection<EditorMenuTraceInfo> getChildren()
        The children collection of the editor menu info node. Commonly it is the info nodes of the next transformation/substitute parts in the menu building chain. For example if the current node is the node provided by the group part then the children nodes are the nodes provided by all the items in the group.
        Returns:
        the children collection editor menu trace info. Always not null.
